1:03:12.958 --> 1:03:14.541
-Is Mona in there?
-Rup.

1:03:14.625 --> 1:03:15.458
Fridge.

1:03:16.333 --> 1:03:17.166
Fridge.

1:03:19.375 --> 1:03:21.375
