in the freakin' fridge?

1:04:30.791 --> 1:04:31.750
[Parm] Sorry, Rup.

1:04:31.833 --> 1:04:33.291
Yeah.

1:04:33.375 --> 1:04:34.208
[Sandy] Thanks Rup.

1:04:34.291 --> 1:04:35.958
[Parm] Sorry.

1:04:36.041 --> 1:04:36.875
Sorry.

1:04:38.833 --> 1:04:40.291
-Here.
-Thanks.

1:04:40.375 --> 1:04:41.375
Yep.

1:04:42.375 --> 1:04:43.291
-Thank you.
-You okay?

1:04:43.375 --> 1:04:44.541
Yeah, I'm great.

1:04:44.625 --> 1:04:45.458
Sorry.

1:04:48.791 --> 1:04:49.750
-[Sandy sighs]
-[door slams]

1:04:49.833 --> 1:04:51.625
Where's the cooker sauce?

1:04:51.708 --> 1:04:53.500
[Parm] Cooker sauce.

1:04:53.583 --> 1:04:57.875
And uh… [in Punjabi] Cover your head.

1:04:57.958 --> 1:05:00.583
[upbeat music plays]

1:05:02.875 --> 1:05:05.333
<i>♪ I have a secret love ♪</i>

1:05:05.416 --> 1:05:10.000
<i>♪ That I know I shouldn't have ♪</i>

1:05:10.083 --> 1:05:14.250
<i>♪ And time and time again ♪</i>

1:05:14.333 --> 1:05:17.166
<i>♪ He tells me the same thing right back ♪</i>

1:05:17.250 --> 1:05:19.000
Hey. Hi.

1:05:22.625 --> 1:05:23.791
-Hi.
-Hi.

1:05:23.875 --> 1:05:24.875
Hi.

1:05:29.208 --> 1:05:30.583
Hi.

1:05:30.666 --> 1:05:32.041
