1:05:50.041 --> 1:05:51.333
Taquerias.

1:05:51.416 --> 1:05:55.750
Sweaty, drunk sex 'til we
run out of money and beer.

1:05:58.541 --> 1:05:59.541
Then what?

1:06:02.666 --> 1:06:03.750
