1:07:04.875 --> 1:07:07.833
At the end of the day, we've
been fucking for three years.

1:07:07.916 --> 1:07:08.750
Mona.

1:07:10.458 --> 1:07:11.541
-Mona.
-Don't.

1:07:11.625 --> 1:07:14.083
Mona, you have been
taking care of your father

1:07:14.166 --> 1:07:15.291
