1:08:23.916 --> 1:08:24.750
Stop it.

1:08:25.625 --> 1:08:26.458
Stop.

1:08:28.333 --> 1:08:31.416
Don't pretend you have integrity.

1:08:31.500 --> 1:08:33.000
You're old, by the way.

1:08:33.083 --> 1:08:36.291
That earring is fooling nobody.

1:08:36.375 --> 1:08:37.375
[door creaks]

1:08:40.458 --> 1:08:41.458
[door thuds]

1:08:46.416 --> 1:08:47.416
[door thuds]

1:08:49.458 --> 1:08:51.291
Where have you been?

1:08:52.666 --> 1:08:53.500
