1:08:55.750 --> 1:08:59.333
[in Punjabi] No!
Not in front of your father!

1:08:59.416 --> 1:09:01.166
[in Punjabi] Why are you fighting
in front of your father?

1:09:01.250 --> 1:09:02.791
[Mona] Get off of me!

1:09:02.875 --> 1:09:04.375
[Rup] Get off of him!

1:09:04.458 --> 1:09:05.291
Ow!

1:09:07.041 --> 1:09:08.791
[Mona] Was it true?

1:09:08.875 --> 1:09:10.333
Is it true you put the will in your name?

1:09:10.416 --> 1:09:11.666
Is that true?

1:09:11.750 --> 1:09:15.000
-Is that true?
-Of course it's not true!

1:09:16.000 --> 1:09:17.916
Yes, it's true.

1:09:18.000 --> 1:09:18.833
What?

1:09:20.625 --> 1:09:21.958
What the hell, Parm?

1:09:22.041 --> 1:09:24.791
I'm not keeping the money.

1:09:24.875 --> 1:09:26.291
