1:09:36.208 --> 1:09:37.791
It was the wrong way to go about it.

1:09:37.875 --> 1:09:39.250
Okay?

1:09:39.333 --> 1:09:41.083
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

1:09:48.625 --> 1:09:50.291
