1:09:50.375 --> 1:09:51.958
-This is the truth, Mona--
-[Mona] No, tell me the truth.

1:09:52.083 --> 1:09:54.083
Why did you do it?
Why did you do this?

1:09:54.166 --> 1:09:57.000
Why did you get Dad to
