1:09:58.833 --> 1:10:00.625
Look at my face!

1:10:00.708 --> 1:10:02.750
What is the real truth?

1:10:02.833 --> 1:10:04.791
Just tell me the truth, Parm, please?

1:10:04.875 --> 1:10:06.791
What do you want me to say, Mona?

1:10:06.875 --> 1:10:08.000
Just tell me the truth.

1:10:08.083 --> 1:10:09.708
-Just tell me the fucking--
-Stop!

1:10:09.791 --> 1:10:11.583
Because your a mess, Mona.
'Cause you're a mess!

1:10:11.666 --> 1:10:13.458
Okay? Is that what you wanna hear?

1:10:13.541 --> 1:10:16.458
You're a fuckin' mess! Okay?

